    <note>Zhong(3) Bing [7023] Zhuang(1) Hui's [545] grandson-in-law, Meng(2) Song's [1364] father-in-law. He was recommended for a court appointment by Zhang(1) Jun [211], but it was obstructed by Qin(1) Gui [8008] and he was sent to Zhenjiang instead. He Yi, Song Zhongxing xingzai zamai wu. . ., 40.2a; Ye Shi, WJ, 13.233-234. See also documentation for probable ancestor, Jian [552]. Zhong Bing, WJ, 4.21a (wife #1, born Chen, who married him at age 18 and died in 1134 at age 40). CBD, 1, 647-8.</note>
